data.description: ** SHORT SALE APPROVED @ $250K - WE CAN CLOSE IN 3 WEEKS ** Welcome to this extraordinary home nestled on a double lot, offering a truly exceptional living experience. With its thoughtfully designed features and prime location, this property is sure to captivate you. Inside, you'll find four spacious bedrooms, providing ample space for relaxation and privacy. Three of the bedrooms are conveniently situated upstairs, while one is located on the main level. The large, updated bathroom adds a touch of luxury to your daily routines. Prepare to be impressed by the newer kitchen, which showcases stunning granite countertops and modern stainless steel appliances. Notable upgrades were made in 2018, including the installation of a new furnace, AC condenser, and water heater, ensuring your comfort and peace of mind year-round. The full basement, featuring a walkout rear exit, offers versatility and potential for additional living space or storage. Outside, the double lot provides a generously sized yard, granting you plenty of space for outdoor activities and potential expansion possibilities. Don't miss your chance to experience the charm and potential of this remarkable property. Schedule a viewing today before it's too late. Located just seconds away from Columbus Park, I-290, Family Dollar, and McKinley School this property offers an unbeatable location that makes commuting, shopping, and entertainment a breeze. Don't miss the opportunity to make this charming brick cottage your new home! Property being sold As-Is.
